{"tid":2091001,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"結婚證書揭露 梁振英妻姓Higgins","createTime":"2020-07-02T12:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T13:44:42.000Z","uid":105567,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"51af1c47f29f49c7ebad4d94ac31539ced0be3af","tid":2091001,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:55:22.000Z","msg":"本報追查唐青儀的身世，發現她年輕時曾跟隨英籍親戚改姓「Higgins」，其間成功入籍英國，婚後又改回中文姓名。有律師估計在英國讀書的唐青儀被英籍親戚收養而入英籍，藉此獲減免學費。唐青儀和特首辦都拒回應改姓原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20120511/large/11la1p101new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120511%2Flarge%2F11la1p101new.jpg&h=910e5788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁振英的太太唐青儀曾神秘改姓，結婚證書上的名字為「HigginsReginaChingYee」（紅框示）及簽名清楚可見是「ReginaHiggins」（藍框示）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120511/16327457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120511%2F16327457&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=ff8682e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120511%2F16327457&h=f77f51f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120511/16327457</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6eYA574.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6eYA574.gif&h=0fbd4c8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"227700e8e5b4acce5fe4ec9e0a4c02a4de0199a8","tid":2091001,"uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mcg8rHC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcg8rHC.png&h=93de9396&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cd5d44887cd75bd08c42553583f6ac3f36648e6","tid":2091001,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedB